Lingua/JA/Romaji version 0.03
=============================

A kana<->romaji converter.  Initial release.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module has no other dependencies.

TESTRO

Enclosed is a sample program to illustrate the use of the module.  
You'll need a terminal capable of displaying Japanese characters,
such as kterm.  Enter romaji at the prompt, and it will be converted
to kana and back.

